{"tid":560402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【真●乜都睇晒！】大媽爬入安檢機 遭警告「輻射大危害身體」","createTime":"2018-02-14T05:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T05:32:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"db728f0575a06dc4e598da656c15b6362d55c1bb","tid":560402,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180213/large/1518523940_ec07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180213%2Flarge%2F1518523940_ec07.jpg&h=5da8bb28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚇死人咩！廣東東莞一名中年女子周日（11日）傍晚6時許，到東莞東火車站準備搭火車，因為擔心隨身的手袋內的財物有任何閃失，竟然連人帶袋爬入X光安檢機，結果顯示器出現人形透視圖，骨骼和身材被照得一清二楚，令女安檢員嚇呆。<br />\n<br />\n據報，當時該女乘客行李需要通過安檢程序，被安檢員提醒要將其隨身手袋也要放入輸送帶上送檢，沒想到她乾脆整人爬上輸送帶過X光機。鐵路公安提醒，X光機內輻射較大，對人體有一定危害，切勿胡亂鑽進。<br />\n<br />\n網民講乜：<br />\n<br />\nHoney岳岳歐尼：安檢機入口的地方本來就有工作人員看着呀，這個女的固然有問題，但看着的人怎麼沒阻止呢！<br />\n<br />\nRebekah1213：現在在安檢口東西被盜的也不少吧？那安檢員怎麼沒能保證顧客的財產安全呢？！<br />\n<br />\nCater：感覺這種損傷可不是錢能補回來的。<br />\n<br />\n不要面子的僵屍粉：有點藝術感哦！<br />\n<br />\n孤獨的貓y：我也注意到了肚子上的肉......肉......<br />\n<br />\n姚大嘴請滾出我國：包裏面有鍋，看身材應該四五十歲左右，可能是打工者，沒接受過甚麼教育，賺錢不多，可以理解，但是這麼做，實在不妥。<br />\n<br />\n強心姬：是甚麼支撐她度過短暫的黑暗！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180213/large/1518523942_1a7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180213%2Flarge%2F1518523942_1a7a.jpg&h=064ee770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180213/large/1518523960_a0f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180213%2Flarge%2F1518523960_a0f5.jpg&h=1d510ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180214/57828798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57828798&d=rwA%2B5pHQ3r474X4t2NstPEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=42207595\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57828798&h=5289ae70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180214/57828798</a>"},{"pid":"2ef22a0e847d1ca94f881129d7b37cfce579640e","tid":560402,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:19:29.000Z","msg":"支那人真係戇撚鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16be6cd0989d0a79c54f7ae4f2aab68ecf99aa70","tid":560402,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:25:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5348427e6d56dd6b3bc0e910e52f5d163f56a6b2","tid":560402,"uid":56623,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:30:17.000Z","msg":"幅x光圖成隻蝗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e84a5964bfc879fa5ecbf881294ed6f68cf8f1e","tid":560402,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5348427e6d56dd6b3bc0e910e52f5d163f56a6b2","tid":560402,"uid":56623,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:30:17.000Z","msg":"幅x光圖成隻蝗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:32:16.000Z","msg":"根本就係"}]}